name: Projecteuler
body:
Project Euler
=============
Solutions to [Project Euler](http://projecteuler.net/)

Language
--------

+ mainly Python
+ C for acceleration

Engines
-------

+ PyPy 4.0.1 (Python 2.7)
+ gcc (with -O3 enabled)
+ My Computer
    - Windows 10 64-bit
    - CPU: Intel® Core™ i5-3210M CPU @ 2.5GHz (2 Cores 4 Threads)
    - RAM: 4GB

Requirements
============
- itertools
- progressbar
- ctypes(with gcc, make)
- fractions
- math
